OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784213294
OL,3,CBaby giraffe born at wildlife park
OL,4,Cnamed after footballer Jude Bellingham
OL,6,FA baby giraffe born at a wildlife park
OL,7,Fin Kent has been named after England
OL,8,Ffootballer Jude Bellingham.
OL,10,FThe Nubian giraffe calf was born on
OL,11,FSaturday 11 July, just hours before
OL,12,FEngland's victory over Norway in the
OL,13,FWorld Cup quarter finals.
OL,15,FJude was given her name after staff at
OL,16,FPort Lympne Hotel and Reserve, in
OL,17,FHythe, voted to honour the England
OL,18,Fmidfielder.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
