PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784213294
OL,3,CBaby giraffe born at wildlife park
OL,4,Cnamed after footballer Jude Bellingham
OL,6,FThe arrival is a major conservation
OL,7,Fmilestone, as Jude is the first
OL,8,Fgiraffe to be born at the park since
OL,9,F2018.
OL,11,FHer birth brings the park's herd to a
OL,12,Ftotal of eight giraffes, made up of
OL,13,Ftwo males and six females.
OL,15,FLike most giraffe calves, Jude was up
OL,16,Fon her feet within hours of being born
OL,17,Fand already stands at an impressive
OL,18,F5ft 8in tall.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784213294
OL,3,CBaby giraffe born at wildlife park
OL,4,Cnamed after footballer Jude Bellingham
OL,6,FJude is spending quality time with her
OL,7,Fmother Leana in the giraffe house,
OL,8,Fwhere experienced keepers and a
OL,9,Fdedicated veterinary team are
OL,10,Fmonitoring them around the clock.
OL,12,FThe giraffe calf is due to make her
OL,13,Fdebut later this month.
OL,15,FTony Kelly, Managing Director, Port
OL,16,FLympne Reserve said: "Welcoming the
OL,17,Ffirst giraffe born at Port Lympne
OL,18,Fsince 2018 is an incredibly special
OL,19,Fmoment, not just for everyone here,
OL,20,Fbut for giraffe conservation in the UK.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784213294
OL,3,CBaby giraffe born at wildlife park
OL,4,Cnamed after footballer Jude Bellingham
OL,6,F"The timing of Jude's arrival, on
OL,7,FSaturday when the nation was
OL,8,Fcelebrating England's World Cup
OL,9,Fsuccess, made the occasion even more
OL,10,Fmemorable.
OL,12,F"These first few weeks are a delicate
OL,13,Ftime for both mum and calf, so we're
OL,14,Fgiving them all the care and space
OL,15,Fthey need.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784213294
OL,3,CBaby giraffe born at wildlife park
OL,4,Cnamed after footballer Jude Bellingham
OL,6,F"Our keepers are with them constantly,
OL,7,Fand although it's still early days,
OL,8,Fwe're delighted with how Jude is
OL,9,Fprogressing, and we look forward to
OL,10,Four guests meeting her later this
OL,11,Fmonth."
OL,13,FNubian giraffes are said to be among
OL,14,Fthe world's most threatened giraffe
OL,15,Fsubspecies, making every successful
OL,16,Fbirth an important contribution to
OL,17,Fhelp safeguard the future of the
OL,18,Fspecies.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
